				span Kaymak
				span.tiny .js
				.doub-logo.icon-logo
			
			.separator

			.description.clearfix
				span Kaymak.js is a lightweight, flexible and multi-device content/image slider.
				br
				span It's only 4kb gziped.
				br
				.devices
					span.icon-devices
				br
				span Plugin dependencies are jQuery, Hammer.js and optionally Transit.js (for css3 transitions)
				br
				span Feel free to fork on #[a(href="https://github.com/doubco/kaymak") Github] #[span.inline-icon.icon-github]
				br
				br
				span You can find demos and snippets on this page. If you want to now more open the source code.
				br
				span It's completely free.

			.separator
	
			.sub-title.clearfix
				span Browser support

			.description.clearfix
				span Safari, Chorme and Firefox
				br
				span also with little glitch works on IE9 and IE10 both desktop and mobile.

